authors: Sterling G. Baird, Hasan M. Sayeed, Taylor D. Sparks
algorithm_long: Fit CrabNet and RooSt using 300 epochs, assign compounds to clusters based on chemical similarity, and choose to use CrabNet or RooSt for each compound based on whether the containing cluster sees overall better performance with CrabNet or RooSt, respectively.
